headline: Ainsley Ierland Joins Vinson & Elkins Aviation Finance Practice in London
summary: By Karen Roman Vinson & Elkins said Ainsley Ierland joined its London’s finance practice as partner, following the addition of partner Harry Upcott to grow the firm’s global aviation finance platform in London, Dublin, and New York. headline: Elliott Investment Management takes stake in Pepsi, sees 50% upside for the stock
summary: The activist investor's $4 billion stake in PepsiCo comes as the soda and snack giant battles slowing demand and fierce competition.
